# ### 12  Planning, Docs & CI Standards

* Phases → epics → tasks; statuses (`to do`, `in progress`, `backlog`, `done`, `blocked`).
* Docs in `_dev/docs/`; auto‑update after merges/deploys.
* PR checklist: lint/format pass, tests green, docs updated, no duplicate run scripts.
